channel.title: Help! Can't login to my account!
channel.description: Alright here's the scoop. I've logged in for the first time into my server. I log out to edit my character's settings (only the player rights, though). Then, I go to log in again, after compiling, and it says it can't connect to the server. I go back to start server again, and when I try to login again, it says that i'm alreasdy logged in. What happening???
